{"tid":2241236,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人大常委會審議國旗國徽法　教育中小學生了解國徽歷史","createTime":"2020-10-13T07:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T07:34:04.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85e8eb81e45656533a1febdb9d1c3629c85f3940","tid":2241236,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"(節錄)<br />\n二次審議稿規定，中小學應當將國徽作為愛國主義教育的重要內容，教育學生了解國徽的歷史和精神內涵。網絡使用的國旗圖案標準版本，在中國人大網和中國政府網上發布，需要懸掛非通用尺度國徽，應當按照通用尺度成比例適當放大或者縮小，並與使用目的、所在建築物、周邊環境相適應。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554473-20201013.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554473-20201013.htm&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbYMqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=2e63a3f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554473-20201013.htm&h=dca55aaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554473-20201013.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n好快到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ae40359ff4321c3d6373b46a2ebe30fbb7549a","tid":2241236,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"習近平上台之後將鄧小平嘅撥亂反正都整走埋，幫自己嘅偶像毛澤東洗白<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/kejiaowen/ql2-01112018104005.html/m0111-ql2p4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fkejiaowen%2Fql2-01112018104005.html%2Fm0111-ql2p4.JPG&h=d484d06e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/kejiaowen/ql2-01112018104005.html/m0111-ql2p5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fkejiaowen%2Fql2-01112018104005.html%2Fm011